description:
Support The Channel Here
https://www.evosounds.com 

In this video, we go over Filters, one of the most important sections in any synthesizer. Filters will bring character, life, and movement to a sound. Filters do this by manipulating frequencies in various ways, which allows us to turn our existing tones into smoother sounds, more agressive sounds, and more interesting to the human ear. 

Serum 2 contains a heavy FILTER line up and we will be going over all of them to explain what they do and how you can use them to create even better sounds.
